{
  "texts": [
    "But issues such as power quality problems, system stability, and low-voltage ride-through are still open research problems.",
    "Therefore, through a literature review the study aims to provide future research agendas, propose new ideas, and help facilitate the shift to renewable energy sources around the world.",
    "This review will be useful for both new and experienced researchers as it highlights the new trends, gaps in the research, and potential areas of future work in order to enhance performance and control of DFIG-based WECS.",
    "These results encourage further research in the improvement of control systems, the application of the work, and collaborations with other countries to advance this important area.",
    "Findings and discussionThe analysis intended to obtain the necessary researches on DFIG-based WECS employing scientometric approach."
  ]
}